  "title": "Wasps-Predators  of  Heliothis  on Pigeonpea",
  "abstract": "Heliothis  armigera.  which  is  the  major  pest of  pigeonpea  in  most  areas  of  the  Old  World, has  many  natural  enemies.  At  ICRISAT  we  are exploring  the  possibilities  for  increasing the  effectiveness of  these  in  reducing the losses  caused  by  this pest.",
